{"type": "article", "id": 28582, "title": "大型吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-23T06:51:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163301yqYI5Anlf76EtTQG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>在 2016 <a href=\"http://basel2016.designmiami.com/\">迈阿密/巴塞尔设计展</a>上，<a href=\"http://gallery-all.com/\">gallery ALL</a> 首次展示了这款由 <a href=\"http://www.jannekyttanen.com/\">Janne Kyttanen</a> 设计的吊灯 Avoid，看起来很有未来感。这个超大型吊灯直径为 1.5 米，灵感来源于李球面几何学（Lie sphere geometry），圆形灯罩的表面被设计成了错综复杂的钻石结构。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163259NjIFqd1ir65P4ncQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163259DsG0JdobR71rMYcO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021633006WbTXfGAgDN27Idn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021633009hGSZr0eWImVxvNT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}